# Cline Rules for SimpleAI WebAdmin

@AGENTS.md - Read project guidelines before making changes

## Quick Reference

### Design System
- Colors: zinc palette (50-950) + blue/purple gradients
- Spacing: Container space-y-10, Grids gap-5/6/7, Cards p-6/7/8
- Shadows: md (default) → lg (hover) → xl (active)
- Border-radius: xl (small) / 2xl (cards) / 3xl (hero)

### Critical Rules
1. Generic examples ONLY - use neutral terms like records, items, users, categories
2. Dark mode support MANDATORY (dark:bg-*, dark:text-*, etc)
3. Responsive design (sm:/lg:/xl: breakpoints)
4. SQL security (only SELECT/SHOW/DESCRIBE/EXPLAIN)

### Common Patterns
- Dashboard widget: rounded-2xl, border, bg-white, p-7, shadow-md, dark:bg-zinc-900
- Toast: useToast() from ToastContext, types: success/error/warning/info
- Connection: <ConnectionStatus type="mysql|api|system" />

### File Locations
- Dashboard: app/(main)/dashboard/page.tsx
- Sidebar: components/Sidebar.tsx
- API: app/api/
- Components: components/
- Utils: lib/

For detailed guidelines, see AGENTS.md
